  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><div role=\"note\" class=\"hatnote navigation-not-searchable\" style=\"font-style: italic;padding-left: 1.6em;margin-bottom: 0.5em;\">For the named hour, see <a href=\"/index.php/Named_hours\" title=\"Named hours\">Named hours</a>.</div>\n<table class=\"infobox\" style=\"min-width:22em;max-width:32em;border-collapse:separate;border-spacing:3px\"><tbody><tr><th colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;font-size:125%;font-weight:bold;background: #B0C4DE; text-align:center;\">Hour of the Wolf</th></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Conflict</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Dance_of_the_Dragons\" title=\"Dance of the Dragons\">Dance of the Dragons</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Date</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/131_AC\" title=\"131 AC\">131&#160;AC</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Place</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/King%27s_Landing\" title=\"King&#39;s Landing\">King's Landing</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Result</th><td>\nDeaths of Lord <a href=\"/index.php/Larys_Strong\" title=\"Larys Strong\">Larys Strong</a> and Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Gyles_Belgrave\" title=\"Gyles Belgrave\">Gyles Belgrave</a><br />End of the <a href=\"/index.php/Dance_of_the_Dragons\" title=\"Dance of the Dragons\">Dance of the Dragons</a></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center\">\n<table style=\"width:100%; text-align:left;\">\n<tbody><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"background-color: #B0C4DE; text-align: center;\"><b>Combatants</b></td></tr><tr><td width=\"50%\" style=\"border-right:1px dotted #aaa;\"><a href=\"/index.php/File:Rhaenyra_Targaryen.svg\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"Rhaenyra Targaryen.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/5/5f/Rhaenyra_Targaryen.svg/30px-Rhaenyra_Targaryen.svg.png\" width=\"30\" height=\"33\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/5/5f/Rhaenyra_Targaryen.svg/45px-Rhaenyra_Targaryen.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/5/5f/Rhaenyra_Targaryen.svg/60px-Rhaenyra_Targaryen.svg.png 2x\" /></a> <b><a href=\"/index.php/Blacks\" title=\"Blacks\">Blacks</a></b>:\n<p><a href=\"/index.php/File:House_Stark.svg\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"House Stark.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/7/7e/House_Stark.svg/30px-House_Stark.svg.png\" width=\"30\" height=\"33\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/7/7e/House_Stark.svg/45px-House_Stark.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/7/7e/House_Stark.svg/60px-House_Stark.svg.png 2x\" /></a> <a href=\"/index.php/North\" title=\"North\">North</a>, led by <a href=\"/index.php/House_Stark\" title=\"House Stark\">House Stark</a>\n</p>\n<ul><li><a href=\"/index.php/File:House_Cerwyn.svg\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"House Cerwyn.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/2/2c/House_Cerwyn.svg/20px-House_Cerwyn.svg.png\" width=\"20\" height=\"22\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/2/2c/House_Cerwyn.svg/30px-House_Cerwyn.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/2/2c/House_Cerwyn.svg/40px-House_Cerwyn.svg.png 2x\" /></a> <a href=\"/index.php/House_Cerwyn\" title=\"House Cerwyn\">House Cerwyn</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/File:House_Flint_of_Flint%27s_Finger.svg\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"House Flint of Flint&#39;s Finger.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/9/99/House_Flint_of_Flint%27s_Finger.svg/20px-House_Flint_of_Flint%27s_Finger.svg.png\" width=\"20\" height=\"22\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/9/99/House_Flint_of_Flint%27s_Finger.svg/30px-House_Flint_of_Flint%27s_Finger.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/9/99/House_Flint_of_Flint%27s_Finger.svg/40px-House_Flint_of_Flint%27s_Finger.svg.png 2x\" /></a> <a href=\"/index.php/House_Flint_of_Flint%27s_Finger\" title=\"House Flint of Flint&#39;s Finger\">House Flint</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/File:House_Hornwood.svg\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"House Hornwood.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/0/03/House_Hornwood.svg/20px-House_Hornwood.svg.png\" width=\"20\" height=\"22\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/0/03/House_Hornwood.svg/30px-House_Hornwood.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/0/03/House_Hornwood.svg/40px-House_Hornwood.svg.png 2x\" /></a> <a href=\"/index.php/House_Hornwood\" title=\"House Hornwood\">House Hornwood</a></li></ul>\n<p><a href